    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You are looking at an absolute gem of a car that\u2019s been pampered since day one. Seriously, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014spotless inside and out, and it drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken so much pride in keeping it perfect, and I\u2019m only letting it go because I need something a bit bigger for the family. If you want that new-car feel without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come check this out. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
