      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 1993 Mazda RX-7 (FD) is a peerless example of rotary performance, featuring the 13B-REW engine with its complex sequential twin-turbocharger system in flawless operating condition. The powerband is smooth and responsive, indicating an airtight vacuum system and optimal solenoid function. The five-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise shifts, paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential for superior power distribution. The lightweight chassis retains its original double-wishbone suspension geometry, delivering the razor-sharp handling the FD is renowned for. With documented high compression and a completely stock engine bay, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to own a technically perfect icon of the golden era of JDM engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Original paint. Full service records available. Smoke-free interior. Showroom condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
