      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; it has been strictly garage-kept and hand-washed only. Inside, the cabin remains in an impeccable state; the premium leather seats are supple without any creasing, the dashboard is free of UV damage, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component and convenience feature functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records documented and available for your review. The engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of leaks or wear. This sale includes the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and all owner\u2019s manuals. If you are looking for a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model, this is the one.",
      "price": 47850.0,
